comment4.params=
comment4.target=boolean\ isOnlyThing()
comment4.text=\n\ Indica\ si\ el\ objeto\ es\ exclusivamente\ una\ cosa\ inanimada\ (no\ viva).\n\ *\ @return\ true\ por\ defecto,\ indicando\ que\ es\ un\ objeto\ inanimado\n
comment5.params=
comment5.target=boolean\ isLivingThing()
comment5.text=\n\ Indica\ si\ el\ objeto\ es\ una\ entidad\ viva\ (LivingThing).\n\ *\ @return\ false\ por\ defecto,\ asumiendo\ que\ las\ cosas\ b\u00E1sicas\ no\ est\u00E1n\ vivas\n
